data.description: Spacious 5 bedroom home with 2 bathrooms, designed with a contemporary open concept. The interior seamlessly integrates the living, dining and kitchen areas creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. Modern finishes and fixtures enhance the stylish aesthetic while the bedrooms provide both comfort and privacy. This home offers a perfect blend of functionality and aesthetic appeal for a modern lifestyle and located in a desirable neighborhood.
